[Cite as 03/11/2003 Case Announcements, 2003-Ohio-1076.]

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

March 11, 2003

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2002-0252. Robinson v. Nationwide Mut. Ins. Co.

Lake App. No. 2001-L-119, 2001-Ohio-8793. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Lake County. Upon consideration of joint application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
